          <li>
            <span
              class="mr-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 px-2 leading-none text-blue-700"
            >&gt;</span>Likes working with open standards and open source tools.</li>
          <li>
            <span
              class="mr-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 px-2 leading-none text-blue-700"
            >&gt;</span>Is detail oriented, communicative and eager to improve data quality.</li>
          <li>
            <span
              class="mr-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 px-2 leading-none text-blue-700"
            >&gt;</span>Wants to learn how to build applications that work with linked data, and is willing to invest time in learning semantic software development.</li>
        </ul>
